[[span class="bigtext st"]]SECTION B:[[/span]] Oriykalkos Data Storage

For non-volatile data storage, LOTUS utilizes a single mass of [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-6500 synthetic oriykalkos][[span class="fnnum"]];[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]//Oriykalkos//, informally known as orichalcum, is a crystal substance with immense electrical, thaumaturgic and digital storage capabilities; samples under a cubic centimetre in size have been capable of storing up to 950 mega-ampere hours and twenty petabytes of data, depending on the purity of the sample. Acroamatic and molecular analysis of these samples has enabled the production of //synthetic oriykalkos//, a mass-producible alternative; although the properties of synthetic oriykalkos are inferior to the original substance, the industrial production of synthetic oriykalkos regularly attains superior purity, enabling it to out-perform genuine samples.[[/span]] which expands as LOTUS' storage requirements increase, thereby functionally granting infinite data storage capabilities; said expansion is extruded into the fourth spatial dimension via [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-3966 SCP-3966-A] to reduce its functional size.[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]To further minimize the necessary growth of the oriykalkos mass, LOTUS utilizes an anomalously high-compression file format synthesized from the greatest-efficiency file compression schemes attained by [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-079 several] [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-6276 self-improving] artificial intelligence programs that were subject to [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-3955 continuous activation over anomalously-extended durations].[[/span]]
----
[[span class="bigtext st"]]SECTION C:[[/span]] [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-6820 P. H. Ontokinetic Sink]

Section C was initially a wired connection to all global networks accessible from [[span class="bigtext"]]##rgb(var(--four-color))|FACILITY-6488##[[/span]]; it has since been replaced with a restricted PH-OS[[span class="fnnum"]];[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]'//In its simplest terms, the Placeholder Ontokinetic Sink reads the sum information of the universe, encoding it into a readable format to allow digital systems to read, react, and alter the narrative-space-time of reality.//' -- [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5242 Dir. Place H. McD.], Esoteric Polymath.[[/span]] unit which permits LOTUS to access the Cybersphere: the sum of all digitally / electronically-stored data.[[span class="fnnum"]];[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]A failsafe feature incorporated into all PH-OS systems prevents them from being used to access or alter each other; as a result, LOTUS is not capable of circumventing Section C's restrictions through using it to access another unrestricted PH-OS unit.[[/span]] LOTUS is entirely composed of such data, ensuring it would be obligated to attempt self-containment in the event of its own deviance.

To minimize the likelihood of LOTUS' activities being monitored or tracked by potentially hostile agents, LOTUS' [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5241 infosignature is encrypted through antimemetic mutation]; this encryption is engineered such that [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1812 individuals with an accurate awareness of LOTUS' true nature and functions are inoculated from the effect].
----
[[span class="bigtext st"]]SECTION D:[[/span]] Dedicated Power Supply & Backup

The hardware of LOTUS is directly powered by a dedicated multi-unit system consisting of:

* Two Generation II [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-2400 Tesla-Anborough Ectoentropic Reactors];
* Four Generation III Foundation [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-2493 Antimatter Reactors];
* Twenty-eight Generation XII Nuclear Reactors;
* Ninety-six Generation IV Leichardt Oriykalkos Power Cells.

For each TAE Reactor disabled, two FAM Reactors must be reactivated, and for each FAM Reactor disabled, seven Nuclear Reactors must be reactivated. LOTUS is connected to the reactors via the LOP Cells; if unreplenished, the LOP Cells are capable of storing and discharging sufficient power to keep LOTUS fully functional for three days.

While active, each FAM Reactor consumes twenty tonnes of baryonic matter daily to maintain maximum output, the content of which must be physically non-anomalous; conversely, TAE Reactors do not require any resource input. An on-site backup reserve of no less than 200 fully-charged LOP Cells are to be maintained concurrently, and must also be inspected twice daily for degradation. A decrease in the net energy stored within all active LOP Cells is indicative of a reduction in power output from any/all active reactor cores, and must be investigated immediately.
----
[[span class="bigtext st"]]SECTION E:[[/span]] Sublunary & [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/acroamatic-abatement Acroamatic Dissipators]

To counteract the buildup of non-anomalous excess heat and anomalous digital data, LOTUS is equipped with a thaumaturgically-reinforced, temporally-accelerated industrial-grade coolant system which immediately redirects all undesired heat, orphic energies, and platonic substances into a network of sublunary & acroamatic dissipators; these dissipators are capable of abating the majority of known esoteric effluence[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]Such as [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/iteration-0 tachyons], [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/spikebrennan-s-proposal akiva radiation], and [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/i-h-p-proposal malignant narrative elements].[[/span]] ​and their effects, and will otherwise contain said effluence for transport to a [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/secure-facility-dossier-site-43 specialized abatement facility].
