On 21/05/2036, Director Isabi was contacted by a future iteration of themself via [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5956 the REISNO Cannon], notifying them of a covert faction of AI entities who had collaborated to access Site-83's Olympos Supercomputer and continuously run antimemetically-encrypted calculations on its systems for several months. Ensuing investigation revealed...
[[/div]]

