* Dir. Yves Isabi;
* Dir. Vandis Kelvin;
* Lord Angus Le Moix;
* ~85 other [[span class="bigtext"]]##rgb(var(--four-color))|A-CLASS##[[/span]] personnel composing the O4 Council;
